              <div className="mt-4 rounded-[20px] border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.025)] p-4 text-sm leading-7 text-[rgba(205,214,225,0.72)]">
                Flow 不进 Notes 的 L1 主位。当前页练的是指板识字、degree 识别、chord tone 识别与反应压力，而不是路径流动。
              </div>
